============================================================
  MATHEMATICS
============================================================

Theorem/Law:  Prime Number Theorem
Branch:       Number Theory
Formula:      π(n) ~ n/ln(n)
Applications: Cryptography, algorithm analysis
Discoverer:   Hadamard/de la VP (1896)

Theorem/Law:  Central Limit Theorem
Branch:       Statistics
Formula:      Sample means approach normal distribution
Applications: Polling, quality control, finance
Discoverer:   Lyapunov (1901)

Theorem/Law:  Fundamental Theorem of Calculus
Branch:       Calculus
Formula:      ∫[a,b] f'(x)dx = f(b) - f(a)
Applications: Physics, engineering, economics
Discoverer:   Newton/Leibniz (1670)

